14 WHEREAS, this outstanding organization has had a tremendous impact on its community
15 through its spirit of service and desire to improve the quality of life in Gwinnett, Georgia;
16 and
17 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that Neighborhood Cooperative Ministries
18 be appropriately honored.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
20 the members of this body recognize and commend Neighborhood Cooperative Ministries for
21 its many valuable contributions on behalf of the citizens of Georgia and extend best wishes
22 for the future.
23 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
24 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to
25 Neighborhood Cooperative Ministries.
